title: CHAD TIM TIM COLLECTION
description:
Introducing the Chad Tim Tim Icon series collection.

As genuine as they come, Chad Tim Tim has become renowned for his classic style on and off the board. We worked with Chad to create his ideal pants that are just as good to chill in as they are to skate in. 

Reinforced crotch seam ensures that your pants wont "blow out" while skating, along with 2% stretch for increased flexibility. To top it off we added Chad's custom "toothpick" 5th pocket. The Chad Tim tim Collection

There's no peace without sacrifice.
